      <div id="features">
        <h2> World-class handicraft products</h2>
        <p>High-quality products that are woven with fair trade principles & holistically-responsible busines practices</p>
        <hr class="title-text-separator"/>
         
         <div>
          <a href="#"><i class="fas fa-key"></i></a>
          <h3>Opportunities for disadvantaged artisans and producers</h3>
          <p>All of the products are made by the marginalized and small producers from the Philippines</p>
         </div>

         <div>
           <a href="#"><i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i></a>
           <h3>Fair Payment</h3>
           <p>The artisans and producers receive fair pay that is mutually negotiated and agreed by all through an on going dialogue and participation</p>
         </div>

         <div>
           <a href="#"><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i></a>
           <h3>Respect for the Environment</h3>
           <p>We maximize the use of raw materials from sustainably managed sources and have the least overall impact on the environment.</p>
         </div>
      </div>

