      <!--JOIN THE BUSINESS REVOLUTION/VIDEO-->
      <div id="#join">
        <h2>Join the Business Revolution</h2>
        <hr class="title-text-separator"/>
        <p>CCAP is composed of a non-government organization(NG0) and a marketing company
          that empower thirty-one (31) community-based marginal producer groups located in
          eleven (11) provinces of the Philippines. The said groups employ a total of around 
          nine-hundred (900) artisans. We are a guaranteed member of the World Fair Trade Organization (WFTO)
          and dedicated to promote Fair Trade.
        </p>
        <div>
          <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/FpuRfIzGw7o" 
